### Update cooperative
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/cooperatives/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Green Valley Cooperative (Updated)",
  "address": "123 Main Street, Springfield, Updated",
  "phone": "+1234567899",
  "founded": "2020-01-15",
  "founder": "Jane Smith",
  "score": 80
}

### Update cooperative score (Assessment)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/cooperatives/1/score
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "score": 92
}

### Update score with validation error (score > 100)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/cooperatives/1/score
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
